values:
I'm such a jerk.&nbsp; I don't even know why I'm such a jerk.&nbsp; I came home to help out around the house and help take care of Ben.&nbsp; And all I do is grumble anytime I have to do anything!&nbsp; And I don't spend much time at all with Ben.&nbsp; I stay back in my room, in my own little world.&nbsp; When he comes back to my room, he just messes stuff up (I have too much stuff in a tiny room) and I always yell at him to get out.&nbsp; Of course, he never listens, so I usually end up taking him back to the front room myself, dropping him off, and giving my mom a look like, "Can't you keep him out here for once??"&nbsp;&nbsp; Gosh I'm a jerk.&nbsp; I see myself doing it and I know how horrible I'm being and I can't stop it.&nbsp; I really don't know what my problem is.&nbsp; 

I need friends.&nbsp;&nbsp; And a life.&nbsp;&nbsp; And my own place.

Really, I just wish I could grow up.&nbsp; It's about time.
